{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🍴 Fork 的真正价值\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Fork 的真正价值，不是"回到过去"。**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **而是："前面昂贵的步骤只做一次，后面便宜的策略同时试很多种。"**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 🎯 场景：AI Bug-Fix Agent\n",
    "\n",
    "你未来想做的 agent 流程：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "检测 UI bug\n",
    "↓\n",
    "分析代码\n",
    "↓\n",
    "生成 fix\n",
    "↓\n",
    "跑 Playwright\n",
    "↓\n",
    "部署到 AI 环境\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Graph 结构：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "START → detect_bug → collect_logs → analyze_repo → generate_fix → run_playwright → deploy\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 💰 前 3 步特别贵！\n",
    "\n",
    "| 步骤 | 操作 | 耗时 |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| step1: detect_bug | screenshots, browser logs, DOM | 20 秒 |\n",
    "| step2: collect_logs | Kibana, Splunk, Datadog | 30 秒 |\n",
    "| step3: analyze_repo | RAG: 200 files, embeddings, vector search | 50 秒 |\n",
    "\n",
    "到这里你已经花了：**100 秒 + $3**\n",
    "\n",
    "checkpoint 保存为 `cp_analyzed`：\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "state = {\n",
    "    \"bug_description\": \"...\",\n",
    "    \"screenshots\": ...,\n",
    "    \"logs\": ...,\n",
    "    \"relevant_files\": ...,\n",
    "}\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🔑 关键一步：`generate_fix`\n",
    "\n",
    "LLM 要写 patch。\n",
    "\n",
    "第一次生成（branch A）：\n",
    "- GPT-4o, temperature=0, prompt v1\n",
    "- 结果：**test failed** ❌"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## ❌ 方案 1：不用 Fork\n",
    "\n",
    "重新跑整个 graph → 又要 detect_bug + collect_logs + analyze_repo\n",
    "\n",
    "再花 **100 秒 + $3**\n",
    "\n",
    "如果试 10 次：**1000 秒 + $30** 😱\n",
    "\n",
    "很蠢。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## ✅ 方案 2：用 Fork\n",
    "\n",
    "从 `cp_analyzed` fork 出多个分支：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "thread 1\n",
    "\n",
    "detect → logs → analyze → cp_analyzed\n",
    "                              ├── branch A: GPT-4o + prompt v1\n",
    "                              ├── branch B: GPT-4o + prompt v2\n",
    "                              ├── branch C: GPT-5 + prompt v2\n",
    "                              └── branch D: Claude + prompt v3\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "前面的 100 秒 **只跑一次**！\n",
    "\n",
    "后面每个 branch 只需要 `generate_fix + run_playwright` ≈ **5 秒**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📊 成本对比\n",
    "\n",
    "| 方案 | 4 个实验的总耗时 | 总成本 |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| ❌ 不用 fork | 400 秒 | $12 |\n",
    "| ✅ 用 fork | 120 秒 | $3.5 |\n",
    "\n",
    "这就是 fork 的巨大价值！🚀"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🔬 更贴近日常的用法\n",
    "\n",
    "同一个 bug context，想试不同策略：\n",
    "\n",
    "**不同 prompt：**\n",
    "- prompt A: \"Fix conservatively\"\n",
    "- prompt B: \"Prefer minimal diff\"\n",
    "- prompt C: \"Prefer accessibility\"\n",
    "\n",
    "**不同 model：**\n",
    "- model A: OpenAI\n",
    "- model B: Anthropic\n",
    "- model C: local model\n",
    "\n",
    "Fork 就是：\n",
    "> **同一个 expensive context，不同 repair strategy 并行实验。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🌿 Git 类比\n",
    "\n",
    "你已经做到 commit C（所有 logs 都收集完了）\n",
    "\n",
    "现在想试：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "branch prompt-v1\n",
    "branch prompt-v2\n",
    "branch prompt-v3\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "而不是每次 `git clone → build → test` 从头开始。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 💡 一句话总结\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Fork 的真正价值，不是"回到过去"。**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **而是："前面昂贵的步骤只做一次，后面便宜的策略同时试很多种。"**\n",
    "\n",
    "对于要做 bug-fix agents / code agents / RAG agents / long workflows 的场景，\n",
    "fork 是非常有 **production 价值** 的功能，不是 toy feature。🎯"
   ]
  }
 ],
